nt-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">（二）服务终止后，</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">MIGO</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">没有义务为用户保留原账号中或与之相关的任何信息，或转发任何未曾阅读或发送的信息给用户或第三方。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">（三）用户理解并同意，即便在本协议终止及用户的服务被终止后，</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">MIGO</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">仍有权：</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">1</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">、继续保存用户的用户信息；</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">2</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">、继续向用户主张在其使用百姓网平台服务期间因违反法律法规、本协议及平台规则而应承担的责任。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">七、服务的变更、中断</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">（一）鉴于网络服务的特殊性，用户需同意</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">MIGO</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">会变更、中断部分或全部的网络服务，并删除（不再保存）用户在使用过程中提交的任何资料，而无需通知用户，也无需对任何用户或任何第三方承担任何责任。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">（二）</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">MIGO</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">需要定期或不定期地对提供网络服务的平台进行检测或者更新，如因此类情况而造成网络服务在合理时间内的中断，</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">MIGO</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">无需为此承担任何责任。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">八、服务条款修改</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">（一）</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">MIGO</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">有权随时修改本服务条款的任何内容，一旦本服务条款的任何内容发生变动，</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">MIGO</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">将会通过适当方式向用户提示修改内容。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">（二）如果不同意</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">MIGO</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">对本服务条款所做的修改，用户有权停止使用网络服务。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">（三）如果用户继续使用网络服务，则视为用户接受</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">MIGO</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">对本服务条款所做的修改。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">九、免责与赔偿声明</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 5.55pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:15.45pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt; font-variant:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline">1.</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">若</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">MIGO</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">已经明示其服务提供方式发生变更并提醒用户应当注意事项，用户未按要求操作所产生的一切后果由用户自行承担。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">（二）用户明确同意其使用</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">MIGO</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">所存在的风险将完全由其自己承担，因其使用</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">MIGO</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">而产生的一切后果也由其自己承担。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">（三）用户同意保障和维护</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">MIGO</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">及其他用户的利益，由于用户在使用</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">MIGO</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">有违法、不真实、不正当、侵犯第三方合法权益的行为，或用户违反本协议项下的任何条款而给</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">MIGO</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">及任何其他第三方造成损失，用户同意承担由此造成的损害赔偿责任。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">十、其他</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">（一）</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">MIGO</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">郑重提醒用户注意本协议中免除</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">MIGO</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">责任和限制用户权利的条款，请用户仔细阅读，自主考虑风险。未成年人应在法定监护人的陪同下阅读本协议。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">（二）本协议的效力、解释及纠纷的解决，适用于中华人民共和国法律。若用户和</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">MIGO</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">之间发生任何纠纷或争议，首先应友好协商解决，协商不成的，用户同意将纠纷或争议提交</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">MIGO</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">住所地有管辖权的人民法院管辖。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">（三）本协议的任何条款无论因何种原因无效或不具可执行性，其余条款仍有效，对双方具有约束力。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">（四）本协议最终解释权归</span><span style="font-family:'PingFang SC Regular'; font-size:10.5pt">MIGO</span><span style="font-fam